                        p
                            | High quality plastic shell, glass top, stainless steel hand shanks, shockproof and durable.
                        p
                            | Put the lamp in the sun, it will be charged, 3 hours lighting once fully charged.
                        p 
                            | Can be charged by AC charging cord. 
                        p 
                            | When stretching it, light will be on, shrinking it back, light will be off.
                        p 
                            | Red indicator displays charging condition.
                        p 
                            | Safety energy saving, portable, high brightness.
                        p 
                            | Used for camping, reading, boating, fishing, car repairs, etc.
                        p 
                            | Waterproof
                        p 
                            | Stainless steel handle and plastic cover resistant to water, suitable for both indoor and outdoor lighting.   
                        h3.my-3 Project Details
                        ul
                            li Best Use: Hiking, Travel, Backpacking, Camping
                            li Features: Portable, Rechargeable, Low Energy Consumption
                            li Power Source: Battery, Solar
                            li Material: Plastic
                            li Functions: Low Power Consumption, Long life, Bright and no Stroboscopic
                            li Power Source: AC Charging, Solar Power
                            li Led Quantity: 6(5LEDS+1W)
                            li Package Contains:
                            li 1x Solar Camping Light(Include the battery)
                            li 1x Charger Cable (AC)
